metadata.name: Soul of Solitude
metadata.description:
We retreated inside that unknown cave.
No harm will find us there.
Here is only us soaking into solitude.
And we hear in silence, the magical whisper talking to us.
Something I had forgotten so far,
That was always with me:
“Soul”
Solitude is the spirituality of the soul.
It is the voice of the self that we have so longed to hear. 
It is the doorway to the mystery that is within us all.
